Information Collection and Use
We collect several types of information to provide and enhance our service focused on Shia books.
Types of Data Collected
Personal Data:
Account Information: To facilitate a personalized experience, we may collect and store basic information when you create an account, including:
Email address
Mobile Number
We are collecting this information to provide you with the following features:
Maintaining a history of your recent book searches
Providing the option to like or dislike books
Creating bookmarks or a wishlist for books
To keep you well-informed about the latest developments and updates
Use of Data
we collect your data to enhance your experience, which includes features like tracking your book searches, providing a book like/dislike option, and enabling you to create bookmarks or a wishlist for books.
Data Security
The security of your data is important to us. We implement appropriate measures to protect it; however, no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.
To remove your account totally from Shia Books, you can log in, navigate to the drawer, and access the 'Settings' option, where you'll find the 'Delete Your Data' feature. It's important to note that once you delete your account, it cannot be restored.
Disclosure of Data
We do not sell or share your basic information with third parties without your consent, except in the following situations:
Legal Requirements:
We may disclose basic information if required to do so by law or in the good faith belief that such action is necessary to comply with legal obligations.
Service Providers:
We may employ third-party companies and individuals to facilitate our Service or provide services on our behalf, such as hosting, maintenance, and analytics. These third parties have access to your basic information only to perform these tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose.
Your Choices
You can manage your preferences and opt-out of certain data collection by adjusting settings within the app.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.